title: Panasonic EH2351AC Heated Eyelash Curling Wand
description: Panasonic Ladies Eyelash Curler, Quick and easy unit that combs curls and separates each lash perfectly, Pain-free, safe and easy to use with no pinching, tugging or pulling, Heat Indicator that lets you know when it's ready to use, Cleaning Brush included, Operates on 1 "AA" battery with up to 42 minutes of usage,

title: 12 - Fancy Swirl Roll On Refillable Glass Perfume Bottle Purse or Travel Size 1/3 oz.
description:
If you are interested in selling perfume or fragrance oils, there are millions of them sold  in these bottles every year. I highly suggest selling the popular roll-ons as a perennial favorite bottle-type.

Once the bottle is filled, the roll-on fits into the top to form a great seal.  They are also very durable- I have shipped many ! They can be carried in a pocket, purse, backpack, glove compartment and never leak.

Whether you are making or filling bottles as part of a business, to make gifts for friends, or for a ritual use, these bottles are among the best!!!
